Hi Mutlu,

The problem is in this line:

y1=c(rnorm(study.nr, mean = eff.size, sd = t2+s2))

Note that 'sd' is for specifying the SD. So it should be:

y1=c(rnorm(study.nr, mean = eff.size, sd = sqrt(t2+s2)))

Then it will work as expected.

Best,
Wolfgang

